
= futurist, pioneer in Creative and Collaborative Economy, designer of the Crie Futuros Movement

URL = http://criefuturos.com/
=Bio=

Futurist, international advisor and speaker, working in four continents, Lala is one of the few world specialists in Creative and Collaborative Economy. She has lectured and worked in four continents, for all the sectors of society that lead sustainable and innovative processes: local and national governments; multilateral institutions; NGOS and networks ; companies and institutions.  Owner of Enthusiasmo Cultural ; leader and creator of the Crie Futuros ( Create Futures) Movement ; Council Member of the National Institute of Fashion & Design, Brasil;  Founder of the Center for Future Studies of the PUC. She designed and coordinates the first Post Grade in Creative and Collaborative Economy  ( Escola Superior de Propaganda e Marketing, ESPM)  to share her methodologies and tools. 

